<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?><root available-locales="en_US" default-locale="en_US"><Summary language-id="en_US"><p>Meet Liferay developers and IT professionals at the sixth Liferay DEVCON in Mainz, Germany! Talk with Liferay engineers from around the world and gain valuable insights for your Liferay projects. Get answers to your questions, learn about new features and use the opportunity to help shape the Liferay community and development in a unique way. You can look forward to a great gathering with lots of knowledge exchange, networking and fun.</p>

<p>As a special highlight we again offer an Unconference on November 18. Here the participants build the agenda at the beginning in a plenary session and then spread out into different discussions. The Unconference offers a special environment for knowledge sharing and targeted exchange with peers.</p>

<p>The Registration page will be online soon! Checkout the Recap page of last year's edition in the meantime: www.liferay.com/devcon&nbsp;</p></Summary></root>
